        benefits: ["metabolism", "cognition", "recovery", "focus"],
        detailedDescription: "Epigallocatechin Gallate (EGCG) is a green tea catechin that activates autophagy and supports cardiometabolic health. It targets Loss of Proteostasis, Disabled Macroautophagy, Mitochondrial Dysfunction, and Chronic Inflammation.",
        synergies: ["Vitamin C"],
