        detailedDescription: "NR is a precursor to Nicotinamide Adenine Dinucleotide (NAD+), a coenzyme essential for metabolism and sirtuin function. It restores cellular NAD+ levels, supporting repair and energy pathways. It impacts Mitochondrial Dysfunction, Genomic Instability, Epigenetic Alterations, and Deregulated Nutrient Sensing.",
